\c 4
\p A
\v 1 Nezuva iro vakadzi vanomwe va
\s " chabata murume mumwe, vachiti, "Tichadya zvokudya zvedu, tichafuka zvokufuka zvedu; tinongoda kudanwa zita rako bedzi; bvisa kunyadzwa kwedu."
\p
\v 2 Nezuva iro bukira raJehovha richanaka nokubwinya, uye zvibereko zvenyika zvichava zvakaisvonaka nezvinorumbidzwa kuna vakapukunyuka valsiraeri.
\v 3 Vakasiyiwa paZioni, navakasara paJerusaremu, ivo vachanzi vatsvene, ani naani akanyorwa pakati pavapenyu muJerusaremu;
\v 4 kana Ishe ashambidza tsvina yavakunda velioni, anatsa ropa reJerusaremu achiribvisa mukati maro, nomweya wokururamisa uye nomweya wokupisa.
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha achasvika pamusoro peimba imwe neimwe pagomo relioni, napamusoro peungano dzaro, gore noutsi masikati, nokupenya kwomoto unopfuta usiku; nokuti pachava nechitaviridzo pamusoro pokubwinya kwose.
\v 6 Kuchavapo netende, richava mumvuri masikati kana zuva richipisa, noutiziro nechivando kana pane dutu nemvura.
